casebody.data:
No. 09-8802. Daniel L. Spuck, Petitioner v. Catherine C. McVey, Chairwoman, Pennsylvania Board of Probation and Parole, et al. 559 U.S. 1034, 130 S. Ct. 2067,

176 L. Ed. 2d 412,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 2790. March 29, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
